#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "Začetek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is a picture of the primary &kaddressbook; user interface before any "
"address data have been entered. The first thing you may want to do is create "
"an address book. Note that the <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> address book "
"is present by default."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je slika primarnega uporabniškega vmesnika &kaddressbook; pred vnosom "
"vseh podatkov o naslovih. Najprej boste morda želeli ustvariti imenik. "
"Upoštevajte, da je imenik <quote>Osebni stiki</quote> privzeto prisoten."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>empty</quote> &GUI; "
"interface</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona <quote>praznega</quote> &GUI; vmesnika "
"&kaddressbook;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>empty</quote> &GUI; "
"interface</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona <quote>praznega</quote> &GUI; vmesnika "
"&kaddressbook;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>empty</quote> &GUI; interface, before any extra "
"address books have been created. The <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> "
"address book is present when &kaddressbook; is first installed."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ov <quote>prazni</quote> &GUI; vmesnik, preden so bili "
"ustvarjeni dodatni imeniki. Imenik <quote>Osebni stiki</quote> je prisoten "
"ob prvi namestitvi programa &kaddressbook;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Add a New Address Book"
msgstr "Kako dodati nov imenik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open &kaddressbook;'s Add Address Book dialog with the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>New&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"folder-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add "
"Address Book...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option. A dialog box will appear."
msgstr ""
"Odprite &kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno Dodaj imenik z možnostjo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Novo&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"folder-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Dodaj "
"imenik...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Pojavilo se bo pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s Add Address Book dialog</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna Dodaj "
"naslov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s Add Address Book dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna Dodaj naslov</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s Add Address Book dialog. Five cloud services are supported, "
"plus three local storage options."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; pogovorno okno Dodaj imenik. Podprtih je pet storitev v "
"oblaku in tri možnosti lokalnega shranjevanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose one of the options that appear in the dialog. Several of these "
"options link to data collections residing in the cloud: <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-dav\"><acronym>DAV</acronym></glossterm> groupware (Distributed "
"Authoring and Versioning, RFC4918), Google Contacts (your gmail.com "
"account), <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-kolab\">Kolab</glossterm> &nbsp;"
"groupware server (collaboration via <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-imap\">&IMAP;"
"</glossterm>), &Microsoft; Exchange Server <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-ews"
"\">EWS</glossterm> &nbsp;(Exchange Web Services, on servers running MS "
"software), and <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-group\">Open-Xchange &nbsp;"
"Groupware &nbsp;Server</glossterm> &nbsp;&nbsp;(an open-source alternative "
"to MS EWS). If you already have access to one or more of these cloud-based "
"resources, you can integrate those data into &nbsp;&kaddressbook; by simply "
"selecting the option and then entering your login credentials."
msgstr ""
"Izberite eno od možnosti, ki se prikažejo v pogovornem oknu. Več teh "
"možnosti je povezanih z zbirkami podatkov v oblaku: <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-dav\"><acronym>DAV</acronym></glossterm> skupinska programska oprema "
"(Distributed Authoring and Versioning, RFC4918), Google Contacts (your gmail."
"com account), <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-kolab\">Kolab</glossterm> &nbsp;"
"groupware server (collaboration via <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-imap\">&IMAP;"
"</glossterm>), &Microsoft; Exchange Server <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-ews"
"\">EWS</glossterm> &nbsp;(Exchange Web Services, na strežnikih, ki imajo MS "
"programsko opremo), and <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-group\">Open-Xchange "
"&nbsp;Groupware &nbsp;Server</glossterm> &nbsp;&nbsp;(odprtokodna "
"alternativa MS EWS). Če že imate dostop do enega ali več teh virov v oblaku, "
"lahko te podatke vključite v &nbsp;&kaddressbook; tako, da preprosto "
"izberete možnost in nato vnesete svoje prijavne podatke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The remaining options in the dialog (Personal Contacts, vCard Directory, and "
"vCard File) all create data sets that are saved on a local storage device. "
"Each one of these options uses the same data format (<filename class="
"\"extension\">.vcf</filename>, or Virtual Card Format), the only difference "
"being in which particular directory the data are saved. The <quote>Personal "
"Contacts</quote> and <quote>vCard Directory</quote> options create a "
"separate file for each named contact you save; the <quote>vCard File</quote> "
"option puts all the data into one file. It's probably easiest to start with "
"the pre-defined <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> address book. You will not "
"need more address books unless you have extensive contact lists you would "
"like to keep separate."
msgstr ""
"Ostale možnosti v pogovornem oknu (Osebni stiki, imenik vCard in datoteka "
"vCard) ustvarijo nabore podatkov, ki se shranijo v lokalno pomnilniško "
"napravo. Vsaka od teh možnosti uporablja enak format podatkov (<filename "
"class=\"extension\">.vcf</filename> ali Virtual Card Format), razlika je le "
"v tem, v kateri imenik so podatki shranjeni. Možnosti <quote>Osebni stiki</"
"quote> in <quote>vCard Imenik</quote> ustvarita ločeno datoteko za vsak "
"shranjeni imenovani stik; z možnostjo <quote> Datoteka vCard</quote> so vsi "
"podatki shranjeni v eni datoteki. Verjetno je najlažje začeti z vnaprej "
"določenim imenikom <quote>Osebni stiki</quote>. Več imenikov ne boste "
"potrebovali, razen če imate obsežne sezname stikov, ki bi jih radi ohranili "
"ločene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have made your selection, click on OK. If you have selected a "
"<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-cloud\">cloud-based service</glossterm> a brief "
"dialog will ensue, to establish communications between <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-akonadi\">&akonadi;</glossterm> (the &PIM; cross-desktop storage "
"service) and the selected cloud server. Here's what the dialog looks like "
"for a Google (gmail.com) account. The other cloud-based services are "
"slightly different, but similar."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete, kliknite OK. Če ste izbrali <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-cloud"
"\">oblačno storitev</glossterm>, bo sledilo kratko pogovorno okno za "
"vzpostavitev komunikacije med <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-akonadi\">&akonadi;"
"</glossterm> (storitev za shranjevanje med namizji &PIM;) in izbranim "
"strežnikom v oblaku. Tukaj je videti pogovorno okno za Googlov račun (gmail."
"com). Druge storitve v oblaku so nekoliko drugačne, vendar podobne."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za povezavo z e-pošto "
"&kaddressbook;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za povezavo z e-pošto "
"&kaddressbook;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog. Begin by clicking <quote>Add</quote>. "
"A new dialog will appear. Once your credentials have been accepted, this "
"screen will reappear, and you will click &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;"
"OK&nbsp;</guibutton>. If you would like &kaddressbook; to refresh the "
"locally cached copy of your contact list automatically, do it here, before "
"you click &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ova povezava do gmail e-pošte pogovornega okna. Najprej "
"kliknite <quote>Dodaj</quote>. Pojavilo se bo novo pogovorno okno. Ko bodo "
"poverilnice sprejete, se bo to okno ponovno prikazalo in kliknite &nbsp;"
"<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton>. Če želite, da &kaddressbook; "
"samodejno osveži lokalno predpomnilniško kopijo seznama stikov, to storite "
"tukaj, preden kliknete &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A second screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Drug posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna "
"Povezava do gmail e-pošte </screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A second screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Drug posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna Povezava "
"do gmail e-pošte</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another picture of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog. Enter your gmail."
"com address and click <guibutton>&nbsp;Next&nbsp;</guibutton>. You will be "
"asked to enter your gmail password."
msgstr ""
"Še ena slika pogovornega okna za povezavo z e-pošto &kaddressbook;. Vnesite "
"svoj naslov gmail.com in kliknite <guibutton>&nbsp;Naprej&nbsp;</guibutton>. "
"Vprašani boste, da vnesete geslo za gmail."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A third screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Tretji posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna "
"Povezava do gmail e-pošte</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A third screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Tretji posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna "
"Povezava do gmail e-pošte</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yet another picture of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog. Your account "
"name and password have been accepted by Google's server. Read the privacy "
"notice and press <guibutton>&nbsp;Allow&nbsp;</guibutton>, then "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton> in the <quote>&nbsp;Add&nbsp;</"
"quote> dialog with which you started."
msgstr ""
"Še ena slika pogovornega okna za povezavo z e-pošto &kaddressbook;. Googlov "
"strežnik je sprejel ime in geslo vašega računa. Preberite obvestilo o "
"zasebnosti in pritisnite <guibutton>&nbsp;Dovoli&nbsp;</guibutton>, nato "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton> v <quote>&nbsp;Dodaj&nbsp;</"
"quote> pogovornem oknu, s katerim ste začeli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter your login credentials as illustrated above and say OK. Voila! Your "
"cloud-based contact list is now integrated into &kaddressbook;."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite svoje prijavne podatke, kot je prikazano zgoraj, in povejte OK. "
"Voila! Vaš seznam stikov v oblaku je zdaj vključen v &kaddressbook;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The &kaddressbook; window after a gmail.com account has been "
"added.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>The &kaddressbook; window after a gmail.com account has been "
"added.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The &kaddressbook; window after a gmail.com account has been added.</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook;ovo okno po tem, ko ste dodali vaš gmail.com e-poštni "
"račun.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another picture of the &nbsp;&kaddressbook; window, after a gmail.com "
"account has been added. You can now manipulate your gmail contacts via "
"&kaddressbook;, if you like."
msgstr ""
"Še ena slika okna &nbsp;&kaddressbook; po dodajanju računa gmail.com. Če "
"želite, lahko zdaj s stiki v storitvi gmail upravljate prek storitve "
"&kaddressbook;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As the preceding screenshot indicates, once you have registered "
"&kaddressbook; as a trusted resource, you can view and edit your gmail "
"contacts using &kaddressbook;. Of course, you may also continue to maintain "
"your contacts by using a web browser, if you wish."
msgstr ""
"Kot je razvidno iz prejšnje slike zaslona, si lahko, ko ste &kaddressbook; "
"registrirali kot zaupanja vreden vir, z uporabo &kaddressbook; ogledate in "
"urejate stike v storitvi gmail. Če želite, lahko stike še naprej vzdržujete "
"tudi s spletnim brskalnikom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you selected one of the local address book options in <link linkend="
"\"select-a-format-step\">step 2</link> above, a different dialog will ensue."
msgstr ""
"Če ste v zgornjem <link linkend=\"select-a-format-step\">koraku 2</link> "
"izbrali eno od možnosti lokalnega imenika, bo sledilo drugačno pogovorno "
"okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal Contacts</"
"quote> dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna "
"<quote>Osebni stiki</quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> "
"dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna <quote>Osebni "
"stiki</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> dialog. You may specify "
"which directory will contain your data, and whether you have write access to "
"this resource, or not. For most people, the default selections (as shown "
"above) work well."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno <quote>Osebni stiki</quote> . Določite "
"lahko, kateri imenik bo vseboval vaše podatke in ali imate dostop do tega "
"vira za pisanje ali ne. Za večino ljudi so privzete izbire (kot je prikazano "
"zgoraj) primerne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make any modifications you deem necessary in the <quote>Personal Contacts</"
"quote> dialog, then click <guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton>. A "
"new address book will appear in the main &kaddressbook; interface window, as "
"shown below."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu <quote>Osebni stiki</quote> vnesite vse spremembe, ki se "
"vam zdijo potrebne, nato pa kliknite <guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</"
"guibutton>. V glavnem oknu vmesnika &kaddressbook; bo prikazan nov imenik, "
"kot je prikazano spodaj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s main window with an empty "
"<quote>Personal Contacts</quote> address book.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Slika glavnega okna &kaddressbook; s praznim <quote>Osebni "
"stiki</quote> imenikom.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s main window with an empty "
"<quote>Personal Contacts</quote> address book.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Slika glavnega okna &kaddressbook; s praznim <quote>Osebni stiki</"
"quote> imenikom.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s main window after the <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> "
"address book has been re-created."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo glavno okno po ponovni ustvaritvi imenika <quote>Osebni "
"stiki</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Add a New Contact"
msgstr "Kako dodati nov stik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open &kaddressbook;'s New Contact dialog by clicking the <guibutton>&nbsp;"
"&plus;&nbsp;New Contact&nbsp;</guibutton> button on the Toolbar. A dialog "
"box will appear."
msgstr ""
"Odprite &kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno Nov stik s klikom na "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Nov stik&nbsp;</guibutton> gumb v orodni "
"vrstici. Pojavilo se bo pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:366 index.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>New Contact</quote> "
"dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega <quote>Nov stik</quote> "
"pogovornega okna.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:372 index.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>New Contact</quote> dialog.</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega <quote>Nov stik</quote> "
"pogovornega okna.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>New Contact</quote> dialog after clicking the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;New Contact&nbsp;</guibutton> button on the "
"Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno <quote>Nov stik</quote> po kliku na gumb "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;Nov stik&nbsp;</guibutton> v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you can see from the preceding screenshot, the <quote>New Contact</quote> "
"dialog allows one to enter several different data items. Additional data may "
"be entered via the <quote>Location</quote>, <quote>Business</quote>, "
"<quote>Personal</quote>, <quote>Notes</quote>, <quote>Custom Fields</quote>, "
"and <quote>Crypto Settings</quote> sub-dialogs, as explained more fully in "
"<link linkend=\"editing-contact-data\">chapter 4</link>, below. For now, "
"let's concentrate on adding the <quote>Contact</quote> data items appearing "
"in the preceding illustration."
msgstr ""
"Kot je razvidno iz prejšnje zaslonske slike, lahko v pogovorno okno "
"<quote>Nov stik</quote> vnesete več različnih podatkovnih elementov. Dodatne "
"podatke lahko vnesete v podpogovorna okna <quote>Lokacija</quote>, "
"<quote>Posel</quote>, <quote>Osebno</quote>, <quote>Opombe</quote>, "
"<quote>Polja po meri</quote> in <quote>Nastavitve šifriranja</quote>, kot je "
"podrobneje razloženo v <link linkend=\"editing-contact-data\">poglavje 4</"
"link>. Za zdaj se osredotočimo na dodajanje podatkovnih elementov "
"<quote>Stik</quote>, ki so prikazani na prejšnji sliki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have created more than one address book, use the drop-down list "
"labeled <quote>Add to:</quote> to select the data set to which the new "
"contact will be added. Then enter the new contact's name in the input field "
"marked <quote>Name</quote>, and key in his or her email address in the input "
"field labeled &nbsp;<quote>Email</quote>. If you want to specify special "
"formatting options for this contact's name data, click the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</guibutton> button to the right of the "
"<quote>Name</quote> input field and follow the prompts. If you wish to add "
"more email addresses for this person, click the <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> button to the right of the <quote>Email</quote> input field and "
"another Email input field will be generated. To delete an Email address, "
"click the associated <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če ste ustvarili več kot en imenik, s spustnim seznamom z oznako "
"<quote>Dodaj v:</quote> izberite nabor podatkov, v katerega bo dodan nov "
"stik. Nato vnesite ime novega stika v vnosno polje z oznako <quote>Ime</"
"quote> in vnesite njegov e-poštni naslov v vnosno polje z oznako &nbsp;"
"<quote>E-pošta</quote>. Če želite določiti posebne možnosti oblikovanja za "
"podatke o imenu tega stika, kliknite gumb <guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> desno od vnosnega polja <quote>Ime</quote> in sledite navodilom. "
"Če želite za to osebo dodati več e-poštnih naslovov, kliknite "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</guibutton> na desni strani vnosnega polja "
"<quote>E-pošta</quote> in ustvarilo se bo še eno vnosno polje e-pošta. Če "
"želite izbrisati e-poštni naslov, kliknite pripadajoči <guibutton>&nbsp;"
"&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may also associate a nickname, one or more telephone numbers, multiple "
"instant messaging services, and several web sites with each contact in an "
"address book, as explained in <link linkend=\"editing-contact-data\">chapter "
"4</link>. You may also use the <quote>Show messages ...</quote> and "
"<quote>Allow remote content ...</quote> options to fine-tune the way &kmail; "
"handles email you receive from each contact. See <link linkend=\"integration-"
"with-other-kde-programs\">chapter 3</link> for a more complete explanation."
msgstr ""
"Z vsakim stikom v imeniku lahko povežete tudi vzdevek, eno ali več "
"telefonskih številk, več storitev takojšnjega sporočanja in več spletnih "
"mest, kot je razloženo v <link linkend=\"editing-contact-data\">poglavju 4</"
"link>. Uporabite lahko tudi možnosti <quote>Pokaži sporočila ...</quote> in "
"<quote>Dovoli oddaljeno vsebino ...</quote>, da natančno prilagodite način, "
"kako &kmail; obravnava e-pošto, ki jo prejmete od vsakega stika. Za "
"podrobnejšo razlago glejte <link linkend=\"integration-with-other-kde-"
"programs\">poglavje 3</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integration With Other &kde; Programs"
msgstr "Integracija z drugimi &kde; programi"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integration Overview -- &kmail;"
msgstr "Pregled integracije -- &kmail;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Because &kaddressbook; -- an essential piece of &PIM;, &kde;'s suite of "
"Personal Information Management programs -- is the central repository for "
"information about all your contacts, it has been integrated into &nbsp;"
"&kmail; and also into &korganizer;. Here is a quick look at the interface "
"between &kaddressbook; and those two programs."
msgstr ""
"Ker je &kaddressbook; - bistveni del &PIM;, &kde;jevega nabora programov za "
"upravljanje osebnih podatkov - osrednje skladišče informacij o vseh vaših "
"stikih, je integriran v &nbsp;&kmail; in tudi v &korganizer;. Tukaj si na "
"hitro oglejte vmesnik med programom &kaddressbook; in tema dvema programoma."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &kaddressbook; from &kmail;'s Tools Menu"
msgstr "Zagon programa &kaddressbook; iz &kmail; menija Orodja"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kmail;'s <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Address Book</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona možnosti <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Imenik</guimenuitem></menuchoice> storitve &kmail;.</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kmail;'s <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Address Book</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona možnosti <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Imenik</guimenuitem></menuchoice> storitve &kmail;.</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launching &kaddressbook; from &kmail;'s <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"address-book-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Address Book</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu choice."
msgstr ""
"Zagon &kaddressbook; iz menijske izbire <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"address-book-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Imenik</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This interface is the epitome of simplicity. Need to consult or update the "
"entry for one of your contacts while reading or composing an email message "
"with &kmail;? Left click <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"address-book-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Address Book</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, and the "
"&kaddressbook; application will be launched automatically, allowing quick "
"access to the contact data you want to view or modify."
msgstr ""
"Ta vmesnik je utelešenje preprostosti. Med branjem ali sestavljanjem e-"
"poštnega sporočila s funkcijo &kmail; želite preveriti ali posodobiti vnos "
"za enega od stikov? Z levim gumbom miške kliknite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"address-book-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Imenik</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in samodejno se bo "
"začela aplikacija &kaddressbook;, ki omogoča hiter dostop do kontaktnih "
"podatkov, ki jih želite pregledati ali spremeniti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Querying &kaddressbook; from &kmail;'s Message Composition Window"
msgstr "Poizvedovanje po &kaddressbook; iz &kmail; okna za sestavo sporočila"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of auto completion from inside &kmail;'s message "
"composition window.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona samodejnega dokončanja iz okna za sestavo "
"sporočila &kmail;.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of auto completion from inside &kmail;'s message "
"composition window.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona samodejnega dokončanja iz okna za sestavo sporočila "
"&kmail;.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using &kaddressbook;'s auto completion feature from inside &kmail;'s message "
"composition window."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba funkcije samodejnega dokončanja v oknu za sestavljanje sporočil "
"&kaddressbook; znotraj okna za sestavljanje sporočil &kmail;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are composing a new email message, &kmail; helps you find the "
"recipient's complete email address by presenting a list of probable matches "
"drawn from the contents of &kaddressbook; and from your email archives, as "
"illustrated above. Just left click an item in the list to use that email "
"address."
msgstr ""
"Ko sestavljate novo e-poštno sporočilo, vam &kmail; pomaga najti celoten e-"
"poštni naslov prejemnika tako, da prikaže seznam verjetnih ujemanj iz "
"vsebine &kaddressbook; in arhiva e-pošte, kot je prikazano zgoraj. Če želite "
"uporabiti ta e-poštni naslov, kliknite levo na element na seznamu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail;'s Recipient Selection Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za izbiro prejemnika v &kmail; e-pošti"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of the recipient selection dialog inside &kmail;'s "
"message composition window.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za izbiro prejemnika v oknu za "
"sestavo sporočila &kmail;.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of the recipient selection dialog inside &kmail;'s "
"message composition window.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za izbiro prejemnika v oknu za "
"sestavo sporočila &kmail;.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting multiple addressees with the recipient selection dialog inside "
"&nbsp;&kmail;'s message composition window."
msgstr ""
"Izbira več naslovnikov s pogovornim oknom za izbiro prejemnika v oknu za "
"sestavo sporočila v &nbsp;&kmail;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are addressing a new email message to multiple recipients, &kmail; "
"provides a convenient method of choosing multiple addressees from the "
"contacts you have saved with &kaddressbook;. Simply left click the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Select ...&nbsp;</guibutton> button to open a Drop Down Box "
"that lists all the contacts in the selected address books. Then scroll "
"through the list (or use the handy <quote>Search:</quote> box), select the "
"recipient you want, and left click &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;Add as To&nbsp;</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>&nbsp;Add as CC&nbsp;</guibutton>, or "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Add as BCC&nbsp;</guibutton> to add this person to the list "
"of email recipients for your new message. Choose <guibutton>&nbsp;Add as "
"Reply-To&nbsp;</guibutton> to insert this address into your message as a "
"<quote>Reply To</quote> tag."
msgstr ""
"Ko novo e-poštno sporočilo naslavljate na več prejemnikov, lahko v programu "
"&kmail; priročno izberete več naslovnikov iz stikov, ki ste jih shranili s "
"programom &kaddressbook;. Preprosto kliknite levi gumb <guibutton>&nbsp;"
"Izberite ...&nbsp;</guibutton>, da odprete spustno okno s seznamom vseh "
"stikov v izbranih imenikih. Nato se pomaknite po seznamu (ali uporabite "
"priročno polje <quote>Poišči:</quote>), izberite želenega prejemnika in "
"kliknite z levim gumbom &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;Dodaj kot Prejemnik&nbsp;</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>&nbsp;Dodaj kot CC prejemnik&nbsp;</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Dodaj kot BCC prejemnik&nbsp;</guibutton>, da to osebo "
"dodate na seznam prejemnikov e-pošte za svoje novo sporočilo. Izberite "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Dodaj kot Odgovor na&nbsp;</guibutton>, da ta naslov "
"vstavite v sporočilo kot oznako <quote>Odgovori na</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail;'s New Contact Creation Interface"
msgstr "&kmail;ov nov vmesnik za ustvarjanje stikov"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of the new contact creation interface inside "
"&kmail;'s message viewing window.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &kmail;ovega novega vmesnika za ustvarjanje "
"stikov znotraj okna za ogled sporočil.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of the new contact creation interface inside &kmail;'s "
"message viewing window.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &kmail;ovega novega vmesnika za ustvarjanje stikov "
"znotraj okna za ogled sporočil.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invoking the new contact creation dialog from &kmail;'s message viewing "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Priklic pogovornega okna za ustvarjanje novega stika iz okna za "
"pregledovanje sporočil v &kmail;u."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you receive an email message from someone who is not yet in your "
"address book, &kmail; makes it very easy to create a new contact. Simply "
"point your cursor at the email address you want to save, then click the "
"&RMB; and a context menu will appear (see above). Select <guimenuitem>&nbsp;"
"&plus; Add to Address Book&nbsp;</guimenuitem> to add the selected email "
"address to one of your address books. If you recognize this person as "
"somebody who's already in your address book, and he is using a new email "
"address, you may click on <guimenuitem>&nbsp;&plus; Add to Existing "
"Contact&nbsp;</guimenuitem> instead -- this enters a dialog that will direct "
"&nbsp;&kaddressbook; to the spot where you want to insert the new email "
"address."
msgstr ""
"Ko prejmete e-poštno sporočilo od osebe, ki še ni v vašem imeniku, lahko s "
"storitvijo &kmail; zelo preprosto ustvarite nov stik. Preprosto usmerite "
"kazalec na e-poštni naslov, ki ga želite shraniti, nato kliknite &RMB; in "
"prikazal se bo kontekstni meni (glejte zgoraj). Izberite <guimenuitem>&nbsp;"
"&plus; Dodaj v imenik&nbsp;</guimenuitem>, da izbrani e-poštni naslov dodate "
"v enega od svojih imenikov. Če to osebo prepoznate kot nekoga, ki je že v "
"vašem imeniku, in uporablja nov e-poštni naslov, lahko namesto tega kliknete "
"<guimenuitem>&nbsp;&plus; Dodaj obstoječemu stiku&nbsp;</guimenuitem> - tako "
"se odpre pogovorno okno, ki bo usmerilo &nbsp;&kaddressbook; na mesto, kamor "
"želite vstaviti nov e-poštni naslov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of the ensuing new contact creation dialog.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za ustvarjanje novega stika.</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of the ensuing new contact creation dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za ustvarjanje novega stika.</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing the address book in which the new contact will be created."
msgstr "Izbira imenika, v katerem bo ustvarjen nov stik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; will ask you to choose the address book to which the new contact "
"should be added."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; vas bo pozval, da izberete imenik, v katerega naj se doda nov stik."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Another screenshot of the ensuing new contact creation dialog.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Druga posenetk zaslona pogovornega okna za ustvarjanje novega "
"stika.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>Another screenshot of the ensuing new contact creation dialog.</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Druga posenetk zaslona pogovornega okna za ustvarjanje novega stika."
"</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deciding if you would like to edit the newly created contact now, or later."
msgstr "Odločite se, ali želite novo ustvarjeni stik urediti zdaj ali pozneje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; will also ask you if you wish to <link linkend=\"editing-contact-data"
"\"> edit the new contact</link> &nbsp;that has just been added. Say "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;Yes&nbsp;</guibutton> if you want to add more data "
"to the new entry right away."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; vas bo tudi vprašal, ali želite <link linkend=\"editing-contact-data"
"\"> urediti novi stik</link> &nbsp;ki ste ga pravkar dodali. Recite "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;Da&nbsp;</guibutton>, če želite novemu vnosu takoj "
"dodati več podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kaddressbook;'s Interface with &korganizer;"
msgstr "&kaddressbook;ov vmesnik s &korganizer;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer;, the &kde; scheduling and calendar management program, allows "
"you to send e-mail messages to people you want to invite to a meeting, and "
"provides two interfaces with &kaddressbook; in this connection."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer;, program za načrtovanje in upravljanje koledarja &kde;, omogoča "
"pošiljanje e-poštnih sporočil osebam, ki jih želite povabiti na sestanek, in "
"v zvezi s tem zagotavlja dva vmesnika z &kaddressbook;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:620 index.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s attendees tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &korganizer;jevega zavihka Udeleženci.</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s attendees tab.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &korganizer;jevega zavihka Udeleženci.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a single attendee to a scheduled meeting in &nbsp;&korganizer;."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje enega udeleženca na načrtovani sestanek v &nbsp;&korganizer;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first interface is just like the <link linkend=\"autocompletion-feature-"
"on-new-email\">auto completion feature</link> provided by &kmail;: just "
"start typing the name of the person you want to invite, and you will be "
"presented with a list of probable matches, as illustrated above."
msgstr ""
"Prvi vmesnik je podoben <link linkend=\"autocompletion-feature-on-new-email"
"\">funkciji samodejnega dokončanja</link>, ki jo zagotavlja &kmail;: začnite "
"tipkati ime osebe, ki jo želite povabiti, in prikazal se vam bo seznam "
"verjetnih zadetkov, kot je prikazano zgoraj."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid "&korganizer;'s attendees tab."
msgstr "&korganizer; zavihek udeleženci."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding multiple attendees to a scheduled meeting in &nbsp;&korganizer;."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje več udeležencev načrtovanemu sestanku v programu &nbsp;"
"&korganizer;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second interface is just like the <link linkend=\"recipient-selection-"
"dialog\">recipient selection dialog</link> &nbsp;provided by &kmail;: when "
"you left click the <guibutton>&nbsp;Select Attendees ...&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"button, a searchable list of the contacts in all your address books will "
"appear, as the preceding screenshot shows."
msgstr ""
"Drugi vmesnik je podoben <link linkend=\"recipient-selection-dialog"
"\">dogovoru za izbiro prejemnika</link> &nbsp;ki ga zagotavlja &kmail;: ko z "
"levim gumbom miške kliknete <guibutton>&nbsp;Izberi udeležence...&nbsp;</"
"guibutton>, se pojavi seznam stikov v vseh vaših imenikih z možnostjo "
"iskanja, kot kaže prejšnja slika zaslona."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding or Editing Contact Data"
msgstr "Dodajanje ali urejanje podatkov o stikih"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Basics"
msgstr "Osnove"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you first click on the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> button on &kaddressbook;'s Toolbar, this screen will appear. "
"(If you click on <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Edit Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;</guibutton>, a similar screen "
"appears, the only difference being that the drop-down box labeled <quote>Add "
"to:</quote> will not appear as part of the <quote>Edit</quote> dialog. That "
"is why both functions are covered in this chapter: they're practically "
"identical.)"
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič kliknete <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Dodaj stik&nbsp;&nbsp;</guibutton> v orodni vrstici "
"&kaddressbook;, se pojavi ta zaslon. (Če kliknete "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Uredi stik&nbsp;"
"&nbsp;</guibutton>, se pojavi podobno okno, s to razliko, da se spustno "
"polje z oznako <quote>Dodaj v:</quote> ne prikaže kot del pogovornega okna "
"<quote>Uredi</quote>. Zato sta obe funkciji obravnavani v tem poglavju: sta "
"praktično enaki.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Add Contact</quote> dialog after clicking the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> button on the Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo <quote>Dodaj stik</quote> pogovorno okno po kliku na gumb "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Dodaj stik&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contact Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Stik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We have already seen (in <link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\">How to "
"Add a New Contact</link>&nbsp;) how basic data like Name and Email are "
"entered when a new contact record is created. Here's a description of the "
"many ways to use the rest of the data fields accessible from the "
"<quote>Contact</quote> tab in the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Videli smo že (v <link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\">Kako dodati nov "
"stik</link>&nbsp;), kako se pri ustvarjanju novega zapisa stika vnesejo "
"osnovni podatki, kot sta ime in e-pošta. Tukaj je opis številnih načinov "
"uporabe preostalih podatkovnih polj, ki so dostopna v zavihku <quote>Stik</"
"quote> v pogovornem oknu "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Dodaj stik&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:713
#, no-c-format
msgid "Phone"
msgstr "Telefon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:713
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may associate one or more telephone numbers with this person. Use the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> and <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> buttons to add or delete phone number fields. The "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Home<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-"
"down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> "
"Drop Down Box allows you to identify fifteen categories of phone numbers "
"(Home, Work, Mobile, Car,<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-isdn\"> <acronym>ISDN</"
"acronym></glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-pcs\"><acronym>PCS</"
"acronym></glossterm>, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"S to osebo lahko povežete eno ali več telefonskih številk. Z gumboma "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> in <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> lahko dodate ali odstranite polja s telefonskimi številkami. V "
"spustnem polju <guibutton>&nbsp;"
"Dom<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> lahko določite "
"petnajst kategorij telefonskih številk (Dom, Delo, Telefon, Avto,<glossterm "
"linkend=\"gloss-isdn\"> <acronym>ISDN</acronym></glossterm>, <glossterm "
"linkend=\"gloss-pcs\"><acronym>PCS</acronym></glossterm>, in tako naprej;)"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Messaging"
msgstr "Sporočanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may associate one or more Instant Messaging service identities with this "
"person. Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> buttons to add or delete "
"messaging service fields. The <guibutton>&nbsp;Select ..."
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> Drop Down Box "
"permits you to identify thirteen categories of IM services: <glossterm "
"linkend=\"gloss-aim\">AIM,</glossterm> Facebook, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-"
"gadu-gadu\">Gadu-Gadu</glossterm>, Google Talk, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-"
"gpws\">GroupWise</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-icq\"><acronym>ICQ</"
"acronym></glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-irc\">&irc;</glossterm>, "
"<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-jabber\">Jabber</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-mnwhl\">Meanwhile</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-sms"
"\"><acronym>SMS</acronym></glossterm>, Skype, Twitter, and Yahoo. (MSN "
"Messenger is still on the list of IM services in version 5.10.3; it has been "
"defunct since 2014.)"
msgstr ""
"S to osebo lahko povežete eno ali več identitet storitve takojšnjega "
"sporočanja. Uporabite gumba <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> za dodajanje ali brisanje polj "
"storitev sporočanja. <guibutton>&nbsp;Izberite ..."
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> V spustnem polju "
"lahko določite trinajst kategorij storitev IM: <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-aim"
"\">AIM,</glossterm> Facebook, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-gadu-gadu\">Gadu-"
"Gadu</glossterm>, Google Talk, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-gpws\">GroupWise</"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-icq\"><acronym>ICQ</acronym></"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-irc\">&irc;</glossterm>, <glossterm "
"linkend=\"gloss-jabber\">Jabber</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-mnwhl"
"\">Meanwhile</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-sms\"><acronym>SMS</"
"acronym></glossterm>, Skype, Twitter, and Yahoo. (MSN Messenger je v "
"različici 5.10.3 še vedno na seznamu storitev IM; od leta 2014 ne deluje "
"več.)"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Web</term>"
msgstr "<term>Web</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may associate one or more web site &URL;s with this person. Use the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> and <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> buttons to add or delete Web address fields. The "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Select ...<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guibutton> Drop Down Box allows you to identify three different kinds of Web "
"addresses: Home, Work, and Other."
msgstr ""
"S to osebo lahko povežete eno ali več spletnih mest &URL;. Z gumboma "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> in <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> lahko dodate ali izbrišete polja spletnega naslova. "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Izberite ...<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guibutton> V spustnem polju lahko določite tri različne vrste spletnih "
"naslovov: Dom, Delo in Drugo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags"
msgstr "Oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may associate one or more Tags of your own devising with this person. "
"Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</guibutton> button to enter the Tag "
"creation and configuration dialog illustrated below."
msgstr ""
"S to osebo lahko povežete eno ali več značk, ki si jih sami izmislite. Z "
"gumbom <guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</guibutton> vstopite v pogovorno okno za "
"ustvarjanje in konfiguracijo oznak, ki je prikazano spodaj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Tags</quote> dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno<quote>Oznake</quote>.</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Tags</quote> dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno<quote>Oznake</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Manage Tags</quote> dialog after clicking the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</guibutton> button next to <quote>Tags</quote>."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno <quote>Upravljanje oznak</quote> po kliku "
"na <guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</guibutton> gumb poleg <quote>Oznake</quote>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags (continued)"
msgstr "Oznake(v nadaljevanju)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;Create new tag&nbsp;</guibutton> button and the "
"data entry field to the left to build your customized list of tags. Select "
"the tags associated with this person from the list appearing in the "
"configuration window. Press the <guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"button to add the selected tags to this contact."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guibutton>&nbsp;Ustvari novo oznako&nbsp;</guibutton> in "
"polje za vnos podatkov na levi strani, da sestavite prilagojen seznam oznak. "
"S seznama v oknu konfiguracije izberite oznake, povezane s to osebo. "
"Pritisnite <guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton>, da dodate izbrane "
"oznake temu stiku."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "Blog Feed"
msgstr "Vir bloga"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this field to record the &URL; associated with this contact's web log, "
"or blog."
msgstr ""
"V to polje vpišite naslov &URL;, povezan s spletnim dnevnikom ali blogom "
"tega stika."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show messages ..."
msgstr "Prikaži sporočila ..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this Drop Down Box to override the corresponding message display option "
"in &kmail;'s <guibutton>&nbsp;Privacy &amp; Security&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"configuration menu. Choose <quote>Default</quote> to leave it up to &kmail;. "
"Choose <quote>Plain Text</quote> or <quote>HTML</quote> if you want to "
"override &kmail;'s default behavior when you receive a message from this "
"person."
msgstr ""
"To spustno polje uporabite za prekritje ustrezne možnosti prikaza sporočila "
"v konfiguracijskem meniju <guibutton>&nbsp;Privatno &amp; Varnost&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> v &kmail;. Izberite <quote>Privzeto</quote>, če želite, da je to "
"odvisno od &kmail;. Izberite <quote>Preprosto besedilo</quote> ali "
"<quote>HTML</quote>, če želite razveljaviti privzeto vedenje &kmail;, ko "
"prejmete sporočilo od te osebe."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow remote content ..."
msgstr "Dovolite oddaljeno vsebino ..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option if you want to override the corresponding message display "
"option in &kmail;'s <guibutton>&nbsp;Privacy &amp; Security&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> configuration menu when you receive a message from this person."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite preklicati ustrezno možnost prikaza sporočila "
"v <guibutton>&nbsp;Privatno &amp; Varnost&nbsp;</guibutton> konfiguracijskem "
"meniju &kmail;, ko prejmete sporočilo od te osebe."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid "&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;"
msgstr "&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to save the changes you have made. This button performs "
"the same function in all seven tabs appearing in the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, da shranite opravljene spremembe. Ta gumb opravlja "
"enako funkcijo v vseh sedmih zavihkih, ki so prikazani v pogovornem oknu "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Dodaj stik&nbsp;&nbsp;</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid "&nbsp;⦸&nbsp;Cancel&nbsp;"
msgstr "&nbsp;⦸&nbsp;Prekliči&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to leave the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Add Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> dialog without saving your changes. This button performs the "
"same function in all seven tabs appearing in the <quote>Add Contact</quote> "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite zapustiti pogovorno okno "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Dodaj stik&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> brez shranjevanja sprememb. Ta gumb opravlja enako funkcijo v "
"vseh sedmih zavihkih v pogovornem oknu <quote>Dodaj stik</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Location Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Lokacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the data input fields in the <quote>Location</quote> tab shown below to "
"associate one or more snail-mail addresses with this person."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite polja za vnos podatkov v zavihku <quote>Lokacija</quote>, ki je "
"prikazan spodaj, da s to osebo povežete enega ali več naslovov polžje pošte."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Location</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Lokacija</quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Location</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Lokacija</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:822
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Location</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add "
"Contact</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"zavihek <quote>Lokacija</quote> v pogovornem oknu <quote>Dodaj stik</quote>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid "(unlabeled) Drop Down Box"
msgstr "(neoznačeno) spustno polje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this list of categories to describe each mailing address for this "
"contact. Available options include &nbsp;<quote>Home</quote>, <quote>Work</"
"quote>, <quote>Postal</quote>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"S tem seznamom kategorij opišite vsak poštni naslov za ta stik. Na voljo so "
"naslednje možnosti: &nbsp;<quote>Dom</quote>, <quote>Delo</quote>, "
"<quote>Pošta</quote> &etc;"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid "Street / Post Office Box / Postal Code / Locality / Region"
msgstr "Ulica / Poštni predal / Poštna številka / Kraj / Regija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use these free-form data fields to enter mailing address data: Street "
"Address, PO Box, ZIP Code, City, and State, respectively, for addresses in "
"the U.S.A."
msgstr ""
"Ta podatkovna polja v prosti obliki uporabite za vnos podatkov o poštnem "
"naslovu: Ulični naslov, poštni predal, poštna številka ZIP, mesto in država "
"(state) za naslove v ZDA."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:842
#, no-c-format
msgid "Country"
msgstr "Država"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this Drop Down Box to select a country, from Afghanistan to Zimbabwe."
msgstr ""
"V tem spustnem oknu lahko izberete državo, od Afganistana do Zimbabveja."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is the preferred address"
msgstr "To je prednostni naslov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this box to designate the preferred, or default, mailing address."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite določiti prednostni ali privzeti poštni naslov."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid "&nbsp;Add Address&nbsp;"
msgstr "&nbsp;Dodaj naslov&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have finished entering address data, left click this button to add "
"a new address to the set of saved addresses appearing in the large display "
"window to the right."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate z vnosom podatkov o naslovu, kliknite ta gumb z levim gumbom, da "
"dodate nov naslov v nabor shranjenih naslovov, ki se prikažejo v velikem "
"oknu na desni strani."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Icon<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-edit.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> in the large display "
"window"
msgstr ""
"Ikona<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-edit.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> v velikem prikaznem "
"oknu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left click this icon to edit the associated address data."
msgstr "Z levim klikom na to ikono lahko urejate povezane podatke o naslovu."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Icon<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> in the large display "
"window"
msgstr ""
"Ikona<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> v velikem prikaznem oknu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:862
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left click this icon to delete the associated address data."
msgstr "Z levim klikom na to ikono izbrišete povezane podatke o naslovu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Business, Personal, and Notes Tabs"
msgstr "Zavihek Poslovanje, Osebno in Opombe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next three tabs in the <quote>Add Contact</quote> dialog are even "
"simpler than the <quote>Location</quote> tab. They allow you to save some "
"information about this person's business and professional affiliations, a "
"few personal details, and miscellaneous free-form notes, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji trije zavihki v pogovornem oknu <quote>Dodaj stik</quote> so še "
"preprostejši kot zavihek <quote>Lokacija</quote>. Omogočata shranjevanje "
"nekaterih informacij o poslovnih in poklicnih povezavah te osebe, nekaj "
"osebnih podatkov in različnih prosto oblikovanih opomb."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:879
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Business</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Poslovanje</quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Business</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Poslovanje</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Business</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add "
"Contact</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"zavihek <quote>Poslovanje</quote>, ki je del pogovornega okna <quote>Dodaj "
"stik</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Business</quote> tab, shown above, lets you save some additional "
"details about this person's professional and business associations. All the "
"input fields are free-form; you may enter any kind of text data in each "
"field. The small <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guibutton> button will open a file search dialog, making "
"it easy to associate a filename with this person's <quote>Free/Busy</quote> "
"schedule, if you wish."
msgstr ""
"Zgoraj prikazani zavihek <quote>Poslovanje</quote> vam omogoča, da shranite "
"nekaj dodatnih podrobnosti o poklicnih in poslovnih združenjih te osebe. Vsa "
"vnosna polja so poljubne oblike; v vsako polje lahko vnesete poljubne "
"besedilne podatke. Mali "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> "
"gumb bo odprl pogovorno okno za iskanje datotek, s katerim boste po želji "
"lahko preprosto povezali ime datoteke z urnikom te osebe <quote>Prosto/"
"Zaposleno</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:904
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Notice that you should enter your business associate's phone as a telephone "
"number under the <quote><link linkend=\"edit-contact-tab\">Contact</link></"
"quote> tab. Similarly, his office address is entered via the "
"<quote>Location</quote> tab, as described in <link linkend=\"edit-location-"
"tab\">the preceding section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da morate v zavihku <quote><link linkend=\"edit-contact-tab"
"\">Stik</link></quote> kot telefonsko številko vnesti telefon svojega "
"poslovnega partnerja. Podobno se naslov njegove pisarne vnese prek zavihka "
"<quote>Lokacija</quote>, kot je opisano v <link linkend=\"edit-location-tab"
"\">prejšnjem razdelku</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:911
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Osebno</quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:917
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Osebno</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add "
"Contact</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Osebno</quote> v pogovornem oknu "
"<quote>Dodaj stik</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this tab to store a few personal details: this person's birthday, his "
"wedding anniversary, and the name of his partner, or significant other. "
"Click one of the buttons (&eg;, <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-birthday.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton>&nbsp;) to enter his date of "
"birth, or his wedding anniversary."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite ta zavihek za shranjevanje nekaj osebnih podatkov: rojstni dan te "
"osebe, njegovo obletnico poroke in ime njegovega partnerja ali druge "
"pomembne osebe.Kliknite enega od gumbov (&eg; "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"view-"
"calendar-birthday.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guibutton>&nbsp;) da vnesete njegov datum rojstva ali obletnice poroke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:938
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Notes</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Opombe</quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:944
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Notes</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Opombe</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Notes</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add Contact</"
"quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Opombe</quote> v pogovornem oknu "
"<quote>Dodaj stik</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Notes</quote> tab provides a totally free-form input area in "
"which you may enter any data you want to associate with this person."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <quote>Opombe</quote> zagotavlja povsem prosto oblikovano vnosno "
"polje, v katerega lahko vnesete vse podatke, ki jih želite povezati s to "
"osebo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tricky Stuff"
msgstr "Zahtevne stvari"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook; provides a couple of more complex data storage features, in "
"addition to the simple functions described in the preceding section."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; poleg preprostih funkcij, opisanih v prejšnjem razdelku, "
"omogoča tudi nekaj bolj zapletenih funkcij za shranjevanje podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:970
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Custom Fields Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Polja po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not happy with the wide array of data items that &kaddressbook; has already "
"pre-programmed for you? Well, you're in luck. Someday -- maybe soon --you "
"may utilize the <quote>Custom Fields</quote> dialog shown below to define "
"and populate as many additional data fields as you can possibly use."
msgstr ""
"Niste zadovoljni s širokim naborom podatkovnih elementov, ki jih je "
"&kaddressbook; že vnaprej programiral za vas? Imate srečo. Nekega dne - "
"morda kmalu - boste morda uporabili pogovorno okno <quote>Polja po meri</"
"quote>, prikazano spodaj, za opredelitev in zapolnitev čim več dodatnih "
"podatkovnih polj, ki jih boste lahko uporabili."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Custom Fields</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Polja po meri</quote>.</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Custom Fields</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Polja po meri</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Custom Fields</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add "
"Contact</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Polja po meri</quote>, ki je del pogovornega "
"okna <quote>Dodaj stik</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is an experimental feature which doesn't yet do anything worth talking "
"about. So I'm not going to say anything else about it."
msgstr ""
"To je eksperimentalna funkcija, ki še ne omogoča ničesar, o čemer bi bilo "
"vredno govoriti. Zato o tem ne bom povedal ničesar več."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Crypto Settings Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Nastavitve šifriranja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Need to send a confidential email message that ought not be read by prying "
"eyes? &kaddressbook; provides a simple way for you to associate "
"cryptographic keys with each person on your mailing list."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poslati zaupno e-poštno sporočilo, ki ga radovedneži ne smejo "
"prebrati? &kaddressbook; zagotavlja preprost način za povezovanje šifriranih "
"ključev z vsako osebo na vašem poštnem seznamu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Crypto Settings</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Nastavitve šifriranja</quote>.</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Crypto Settings</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Nastavitve šifriranja</quote>.</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Crypto Settings</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add "
"Contact</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ov zavihek <quote>Nastavitve šifriranja</quote> (Nastavitve "
"šifriranja), ki je del pogovornega okna <quote>Add Contact</quote> (Dodaj "
"stik)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allowed Protocols"
msgstr "Dovoljeni protokoli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose which mode of encryption you wish to use when sending a message to "
"this person: <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-inline-pgp\">Inline OpenPGP</"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-open-pgp\">OpenPGP/&MIME;</"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-mime\"><acronym>S/MIME</acronym> </"
"glossterm>, or <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-opaque\"><acronym>S/MIME</acronym> "
"Opaque</glossterm>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, kateri način šifriranja želite uporabiti pri pošiljanju sporočila "
"tej osebi: <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-inline-pgp\">Inline OpenPGP</"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-open-pgp\">OpenPGP/&MIME;</"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-mime\"><acronym>S/MIME</acronym> </"
"glossterm> ali <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-opaque\"><acronym>S/MIME</acronym> "
"Opaque</glossterm>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preferred OpenPGP Encryption Key:"
msgstr "Prednostni šifrirni ključ OpenPGP:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;Change...&nbsp;</guibutton> button to select from a "
"list of available Open<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-pgp\">PGP</glossterm> keys, "
"if you have chosen OpenPGP encryption. Use the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guibutton> button "
"to clear a previously selected key."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>&nbsp;Spremeni...&nbsp;</guibutton> izberite s seznama "
"razpoložljivih ključev Open<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-pgp\">PGP</glossterm>, "
"če ste izbrali šifriranje OpenPGP. Uporabite gumb "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guibutton>, da "
"počistite predhodno izbrani ključ."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preferred <acronym>S/MIME</acronym> Encryption Certificate:"
msgstr "Prednostno <acronym>S/MIME</acronym> Šifrirno potrdilo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;Change...&nbsp;</guibutton> button to select from a "
"list of available certificates, if you are using a verified key. Use the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> button "
"to clear a previously selected key."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>&nbsp;Spremeni...&nbsp;</guibutton> izberite s seznama "
"razpoložljivih potrdil, če uporabljate preverjen ključ. Uporabite gumb "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton>, da "
"počistite predhodno izbrani ključ."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Preference / Sign:"
msgstr "Sporočilna prednost / podpis :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this drop-down box to specify when messages addressed to this person "
"should bear your cryptographic signature: Never / Always / If Possible / Ask."
msgstr ""
"S tem spustnim oknom določite, kdaj naj bodo sporočila, naslovljena na to "
"osebo, opremljena z vašim kriptografskim podpisom: Nikoli / Vedno / Če je "
"mogoče / Vprašaj."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Preference / Encrypt:"
msgstr "Prednost sporočila / šifriranje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this drop-down box to specify when messages addressed to this person "
"should be encrypted by using the selected protocol and key: Never / Always / "
"If Possible / Ask."
msgstr ""
"S tem spustnim poljem določite, kdaj naj se sporočila, naslovljena na to "
"osebo, šifrirajo z uporabo izbranega protokola in ključa: Nikoli / Vedno / "
"Če je mogoče / Vprašaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1068
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menu Bar"
msgstr "Menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is a rundown of the seven menus appearing on &kaddressbook;'s Menubar."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je opis sedmih menijev, ki se pojavljajo v menijski vrstici "
"&kaddressbook;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>File</quote> menu.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega menija <quote>Datoteka</"
"quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1084
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>File</quote> menu.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega menija <quote>Datoteka</quote>."
"</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>File</quote> menu after clicking the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu></menuchoice> button on the Menubar."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ov <quote>Datoteka</quote> meni po kliku na gumb "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu></menuchoice> na menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu></menuchoice> menu lets you access "
"six main functions, three of which have several options."
msgstr ""
"V meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu></menuchoice> lahko "
"dostopate do šestih glavnih funkcij, od katerih imajo tri več možnosti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>New&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>New "
"Contact</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Novo&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Nov stik</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This has exactly the same effect as clicking the <guibutton>&nbsp; &plus;"
"&nbsp;New Contact&nbsp;</guibutton> button on the Toolbar. See <link linkend="
"\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\">chapter 2 above</link> for complete details."
msgstr ""
"To ima popolnoma enak učinek kot klik na <guibutton>&nbsp; &plus;&nbsp;Nov "
"stikt&nbsp;</guibutton> v orodni vrstici. Za vse podrobnosti glejte <link "
"linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\">poglavje 2 zgoraj</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>New&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"user-group-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>New "
"Group</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Novo&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"user-group-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Nova skupina</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog in which you may define a new group, or mailing list. See "
"&nbsp;<link linkend=\"file-new-group\">the appendix</link> for a detailed "
"explanation of this function."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko določite novo skupino ali poštni "
"seznam. Za podrobno razlago te funkcije glejte &nbsp;<link linkend=\"file-"
"new-group\">priponkao</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"folder-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add "
"Address Book</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"folder-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Dodaj "
"imenik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the <quote>Add Address Book</quote> dialog, which is fully "
"documented in &nbsp;<link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-address-book\">chapter "
"2 above</link>."
msgstr ""
"To odpre pogovorno okno <quote>Dodaj imenik</quote>, ki je v celoti "
"dokumentirano v &nbsp;<link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-address-book"
"\">poglavje 2 zgoraj</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import from LDAP server ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Uvozi&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi iz LDAP strežnika ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to import data from an <acronym>LDAP</acronym> "
"server. The server must be configured before you can use this function. See "
"<link linkend=\"configure-ldap-server\">the appendix</link> for full details."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija omogoča uvoz podatkov iz strežnika <acronym>LDAP</acronym>. Pred "
"uporabo te funkcije je treba konfigurirati strežnik. Za vse podrobnosti "
"glejte <link linkend=\"configure-ldap-server\">priponko</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import CSV file ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Uvozi&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi CSV datoteko ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to import contact data from a comma separated "
"values (<acronym>csv</acronym>) file. A dialog ensues, in which you may "
"associate each field in the input file with a named field in "
"&kaddressbook;'s internal storage record. See <link linkend=\"import-csv-data"
"\">the appendix</link> for a more detailed explanation."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija omogoča uvoz podatkov o stikih iz datoteke z vrednostmi, "
"ločenimi z vejico (<acronym>csv</acronym>). Sledi pogovorno okno, v katerem "
"lahko vsako polje v vhodni datoteki povežete z imenovanim poljem v notranjem "
"zapisu za shranjevanje v &kaddressbook;. Za podrobnejšo razlago glejte <link "
"linkend=\"import-csv-data\">priponko</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import vCard ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Uvozi&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi vCard ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function facilitates the importation of <acronym>vcf</acronym>, or "
"vCard, data. All three versions of vCard are supported. You can learn more "
"about the vCard formats <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VCard"
"\">at this web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija olajša uvoz podatkov <acronym>vcf</acronym> ali vCard. Podprte "
"so vse tri različice programa vCard. Več o formatih vCard lahko izveste "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VCard\">na tem spletnem mestu</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export CSV file ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Izvoz&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Izvoz datoteke CSV ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to export selected contact data as a Comma "
"Separated Values (<acronym>csv</acronym>) file. There are 47 fields in the "
"output record. Please refer to <link linkend=\"export-csv-data\">the "
"appendix</link> for a list of those data fields."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija omogoča izvoz izbranih podatkov o stikih kot datoteke z "
"vrednostmi, ločenimi z vejico (<acronym>csv</acronym>). V izhodnem zapisu je "
"47 polj. Seznam teh podatkovnih polj najdete v <link linkend=\"export-csv-"
"data\">v dodatku</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export vCard 4.0 ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Izvoz&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export vCard 4.0 ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to export selected contact data as a file in "
"<acronym>vCard 4.0</acronym> format. See <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/VCard\">this Wikipedia article</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija omogoča izvoz izbranih podatkov o stikih kot datoteke v formatu "
"<acronym>vCard 4.0</acronym>. Več informacij najdete v <ulink url=\"https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VCard\">članku na Wikipediji</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export vCard 3.0 ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Izvoz&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export vCard 3.0 ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to export selected contact data as a file in "
"<acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym> format. This format is similar to "
"<acronym>vCard 4.0</acronym> format."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija omogoča izvoz izbranih podatkov o stikih kot datoteke v formatu "
"<acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym>. Ta format je podoben formatu <acronym>vCard "
"4.0</acronym>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export vCard 2.1 ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Izvoz&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export vCard 2.1 ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to export selected contact data as a file in "
"<acronym>vCard 2.1</acronym> format. This format is similar to "
"<acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym> format."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija omogoča izvoz izbranih podatkov o stikih kot datoteke v formatu "
"<acronym>vCard 2.1</acronym>. Ta format je podoben formatu <acronym>vCard "
"3.0</acronym>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"print.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Print</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"print.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Tiskaj</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a printer selection dialog. Use the "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"document-preview-archive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Print Preview</guisubmenu></menuchoice> dialog below to "
"set up the range of names and the print format before you select this "
"function."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno za izbiro tiskalnika. Uporabite spodnje pogovorno okno "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"document-preview-archive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Predogled tiskanja</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, da nastavite "
"obseg imen in obliko tiskanja, preden izberete to funkcijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-preview-archive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Print Preview</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-preview-archive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Predogled tiskanja</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a print preview dialog, which also permits you to format the report, "
"select which items to include, and specify a sort order, &etc; See &nbsp;"
"<link linkend=\"file-print-preview\">the appendix</link> for further details."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno za predogled tiskanja, ki omogoča tudi oblikovanje "
"poročila, izbiro elementov, ki jih želite vključiti, in določitev vrstnega "
"reda itd.; Za več podrobnosti glejte &nbsp;<link linkend=\"file-print-preview"
"\">priponko</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"application-"
"exit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Quit</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"application-"
"exit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Izhod</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes the &kaddressbook; application."
msgstr "Zapre &kaddressbook; aplikacijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Uredi"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Edit</quote> menu.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega menija <quote>Uredi</quote>."
"</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Edit</quote> menu.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega menija <quote>Uredi</quote>.</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Edit</quote> menu after clicking the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu></menuchoice> button on the Menubar."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ov meni <quote>Uredi</quote> po kliku na gumb "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu></menuchoice> na menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu></menuchoice> menu lets you access "
"eight main functions, two of which have multiple options."
msgstr ""
"V meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu></menuchoice> lahko dostopate "
"do osmih glavnih funkcij, od katerih imata dve več možnosti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Edit "
"Contact ...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Uredi stik ...</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This has nearly the same effect as clicking the <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;"
"New Contact&nbsp;</guibutton> button on the Toolbar. The difference is that "
"this menu item allows you to edit a contact record that already exists, "
"instead of creating a brand new one. See <link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-"
"contact\">chapter 2 above</link> for complete details."
msgstr ""
"To ima skoraj enak učinek kot klik na <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;Nov "
"stik&nbsp;</guibutton> v orodni vrstici. Razlika je v tem, da ta element "
"menija omogoča urejanje že obstoječega zapisa stika, namesto da bi ustvarili "
"popolnoma novega. Za vse podrobnosti glejte <link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-"
"contact\">poglavje 2 zgoraj</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-cut.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Cut Contact ...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-cut.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Izreži stik ...</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Performs a <quote>Cut</quote> operation on the selected contact. A copy of "
"this contact, in <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-vcf\"><acronym>vCard 3.0</"
"acronym></glossterm> format, is placed on the clipboard. The <quote>Cut</"
"quote> will be completed when you <quote>Paste</quote> this contact "
"somewhere."
msgstr ""
"Izvede operacijo <quote>Izreži</quote> na izbranem stiku. Kopija tega stika "
"v obliki <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-vcf\"><acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym></"
"glossterm> se namesti v odložišče. Funkcija <quote>Izreži</quote> bo "
"dokončana, ko boste <quote>Prilepi</quote> ta stik nekam prilepili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Copy "
"Contact ...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Kopiraj "
"stik ...</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Places a copy of this contact on the clipboard, so you can paste it "
"somewhere else."
msgstr ""
"Kopijo tega stika namesti v odložišče, tako da ga lahko prilepite kam drugam."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-paste.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Paste</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-paste.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Prilepi</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Pastes</quote> the cut or copied contact at the current location. "
"This may be in the same address book you did the <quote>Cut</quote> or "
"<quote>Copy</quote> from, or in another address book. Since the preceding "
"operations placed the contact information on the system's clipboard, you may "
"also paste it somewhere else besides &kaddressbook; (&eg; into a text "
"editor, or as a <acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym> file in your home folder)."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Prilepi</quote> izrezani ali kopirani stik na trenutno lokacijo. Ta "
"je lahko v istem imeniku, iz katerega ste opravili <quote>Izreži</quote> ali "
"<quote>Kopiraj</quote>, ali v drugem imeniku. Ker so se s prejšnjimi "
"postopki kontaktni podatki prenesli v sistemsko odložišče, jih lahko poleg "
"&kaddressbook; prilepite tudi kam drugam (&eg; v urejevalnik besedila ali "
"kot datoteko <acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym> v domačo mapo)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Copy "
"Contact To &nbsp; &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>(a variable list)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Kopiraj "
"stik v  &nbsp; &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>(seznam spremenljivk</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Combines the <quote>Copy</quote> and <quote>Paste</quote> operations into a "
"single click of the &LMB;. The list of destinations displayed depends on how "
"many address books you have created."
msgstr ""
"Združuje operaciji <quote>Kopiraj</quote> in <quote>Prilepi</quote> v en sam "
"klik gumba &LMB;. Seznam prikazanih destinacij je odvisen od tega, koliko "
"imenikov ste ustvarili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-"
"jump.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Move Contact "
"To &nbsp; &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>(a variable list)</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-"
"jump.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Premakni stik "
"v &nbsp; &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>(seznam spremenljivk)</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Works just like the <quote>Copy Contact To</quote> operation described "
"above, except that it combines <quote>Cut</quote> and <quote>Paste</quote> "
"into a single click of the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Deluje enako kot zgoraj opisana operacija <quote>Kopiraj stik v</quote>, le "
"da združuje <quote>Izreži</quote> in <quote>Prilepi</quote> v en sam klik "
"gumba &LMB;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"press\">&Del;</keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Delete Contact</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"press\">&Del;</keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Izbriši stik</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the selected contact from the current address book."
msgstr "Izbris izbranega stika z trenutnega imenika."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Delete "
"Address Book</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Izbriši imenik</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete the current address book. Be careful with this command -- you could "
"lose some data! In theory, this function simply removes the symbolic link "
"between &kaddressbook; and the associated <acronym>vCard</acronym> file or "
"directory (or the hyperlink to a <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-cloud\">cloud-"
"based service</glossterm>), and the real data will not be altered. Still, "
"it's probably wisest to make a backup copy of this address book somewhere "
"before you delete it."
msgstr ""
"Brisanje trenutnega imenika. Pri tem ukazu bodite previdni - lahko izgubite "
"nekaj podatkov! Teoretično ta funkcija preprosto odstrani simbolno povezavo "
"med &kaddressbook; in povezano datoteko ali imenikom <acronym>vCard</"
"acronym> (ali hiperpovezavo na <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-cloud\">oblačno "
"storitev</glossterm>), pri čemer se pravi podatki ne spremenijo. Kljub temu "
"je verjetno najpametneje, da pred izbrisom imenika naredite varnostno kopijo "
"tega imenika."

