#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu></menuchoice> menu lets you access "
"two data management functions."
msgstr ""
"V meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu></menuchoice> lahko dostopate "
"do dveh funkcij za upravljanje podatkov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1442
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>Merge Contacts...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guisubmenu>Združi stike...</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tool allows you to merge the contents of two or more &kaddressbook; "
"records. To activate it, you must first select two or more contacts (hold "
"&Ctrl; or &Shift; and left-click contacts to make your selection). A dialog "
"box will appear, asking you to verify which contacts you wish to combine, "
"and where the merged record should be saved. Click <quote>merge</quote> to "
"complete the operation."
msgstr ""
"S tem orodjem lahko združite vsebino dveh ali več zapisov. Če jo želite "
"aktivirati, morate najprej izbrati dva ali več stikov (pridržite &Ctrl; ali "
"&Shift; in z levim gumbom miške kliknite stike). Pojavilo se bo pogovorno "
"okno, v katerem boste morali preveriti, katere stike želite združiti in kam "
"shraniti združeni zapis. Kliknite <quote>Združi</quote>, da dokončate "
"operacijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1450
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>Search Duplicate Contacts...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guisubmenu>Poišči podvojene stike...</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tool will search one or more address books for duplicate entries, and "
"offer you the option of merging any duplicate records it finds."
msgstr ""
"To orodje bo v enem ali več imenikih poiskalo podvojene vnose in vam "
"ponudilo možnost združitve vseh najdenih podvojenih zapisov."

