"to?</guisubmenu></menuchoice><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F1</"
"keycap></keycombo>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is &kaddressbook;'s built-in help tool. Left-click this option, then "
"move your cursor and click on any one of the first four items on the "
"Toolbar. A brief description of that tool's function will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"To je orodje za pomoč, ki je vgrajeno v &kaddressbook;. To možnost kliknite "
"z levim gumbom miške, nato pa premaknite kazalec in kliknite katerega koli "
"od prvih štirih elementov v orodni vrstici. Prikaže se kratek opis funkcije "
"tega orodja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"tools-report-bug.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Report Bug</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"tools-report-bug.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Prijavi napako</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option opens a dialog that helps you file a bug report at <ulink url="
"\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">bugs.kde.org</ulink>, &kde;'s main bug tracking "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost odpre pogovorno okno, ki vam pomaga vložiti poročilo o napaki na "
"<ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">bugs.kde.org</ulink>, glavno stran "
"&kde; za sledenje napak."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"application-x-ms-shortcut.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Donate</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"application-x-ms-shortcut.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Doniraj</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens a <ulink url=\"https://kde.org/community/donations/?"
"app=kaddressbook\">web page</ulink> in your browser, where you may donate "
"money to support &kde;. We accept euros, dollars, rubles, sterling, yen, "
"yuan, pesos, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"V brskalniku se odpre <ulink url=\"https://kde.org/community/donations/?"
"app=kaddressbook\">spletna stran</ulink>, na kateri lahko donirate denar za "
"podporo &kde;. Sprejemamo evre, dolarje, rublje, britanske funte, jene, "
"juane, peso in druge;"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"change-language.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Switch Application Language</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"change-language.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Zamenjaj jezik aplikacije</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you change the language that is used to label the various "
"menu items and built-in help screens. You must quit &kaddressbook; and "
"restart it before the new language takes effect."
msgstr ""
"S to možnostjo lahko spremenite jezik, ki se uporablja za označevanje "
"različnih elementov menija in vgrajenih zaslonov pomoči. Preden začne "
"veljati novi jezik, morate zaključiti program &kaddressbook; in ga znova "
"zagnati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"kaddressbook.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>About "
"&kaddressbook;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"kaddressbook.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>O "
"&kaddressbook;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on this item to learn which release of &kaddressbook; you're running, "
"which libraries were used to compile / build the executable code, and who "
"the lead &kde; programmer is."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na ta element boste izvedeli, katero izdajo &kaddressbook; "
"uporabljate, katere knjižnice so bile uporabljene za sestavljanje/izgradnjo "
"izvršljive kode in kdo je vodilni programer &kde;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"KDE_logo.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>About "
"&kde;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"KDE_logo.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>O &kde;</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1609
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option displays information about &kde;. Be free!"
msgstr "Ta možnost prikaže informacije o &kde;. Bodite svobodni!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1619
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tool Bar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are five separate tools available on &kaddressbook;'s Toolbar: "
"<quote>New Contact</quote>, <quote>New Group</quote>, <quote>Edit Contact</"
"quote>, <quote>Search...</quote>, and a category filter. Here's a picture. "
"(Note that I have only documented the default version of &kaddressbook;'s "
"Toolbar. You may alter the Toolbar layout by using the <link linkend=\"the-"
"settings-menu\"> <quote>Settings</quote></link> menu, if you so desire.)"
msgstr ""
"V orodni vrstici &kaddressbook; je na voljo pet ločenih orodij: <quote>Nov "
"stik</quote>, <quote>Nova skupina</quote>, <quote>Urejanje stika</quote>, "
"<quote>Poišči...</quote> in filter kategorij. Tukaj je slika. (Upoštevajte, "
"da sem dokumentiral samo privzeto različico orodne vrstice &kaddressbook;. "
"Če želite, lahko spremenite postavitev orodne vrstice z uporabo menija <link "
"linkend=\"the-settings-menu\"> <quote>Nastavitve</quote></link>.)"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1628
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>A closeup of &kaddressbook;'s Toolbar.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Prikaz orodne vrstice &kaddressbook;.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1634
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A closeup of &kaddressbook;'s Toolbar.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Prikaz orodne vrstice &kaddressbook;.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1637
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kaddressbook;'s standard Toolbar, up close and personal."
msgstr "Standardna orodna vrstica &kaddressbook; od blizu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1649
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Contact"
msgstr "Nov stik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This Toolbar button opens the <quote>Add New Contact</quote> dialog "
"documented in <link linkend=\"edit-basic-info\">chapter 4</link>, above."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb orodne vrstice odpre pogovorno okno <quote>Dodaj nov stik</quote>, "
"dokumentirano v <link linkend=\"edit-basic-info\">poglavju 4</link> zgoraj."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1656
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Group"
msgstr "Nova skupina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This Toolbar button opens the <quote>Add New Group</quote> dialog documented "
"in <link linkend=\"file-new-group\">the appendix</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb orodne vrstice odpre pogovorno okno <quote>Dodaj novo skupino</"
"quote>, dokumentirano v <link linkend=\"file-new-group\">priponki</link>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1663
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Contact"
msgstr "Uredi stik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This Toolbar button opens the <quote>Edit Contact</quote> dialog documented "
"in <link linkend=\"edit-basic-info\">chapter 4</link>, above."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb orodne vrstice odpre pogovorno okno <quote>Uredi stik</quote>, "
"dokumentirano v <link linkend=\"edit-basic-info\">poglavju 4</link> zgoraj."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[ Search...&nbsp;<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Q</keycap></"
"keycombo> ]"
msgstr ""
"[ Išči...&nbsp;<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Q</keycap></"
"keycombo> ]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tool searches through all the contacts in selected address books as you "
"type. Pressing <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> simply positions "
"the cursor inside the <quote>Search...</quote> box. Be aware that this "
"function searches the entirety of each contact record; a search for "
"<quote>and</quote> may return not only Andy Brown and Andrew Jones, but also "
"Bill Smith (who happens to work for Brown and Root Construction Company)."
msgstr ""
"To orodje med pisanjem išče po vseh stikih v izbranih imenikih. S pritiskom "
"na <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> preprosto postavite kazalec "
"v polje <quote>Išči...</quote>. Zavedajte se, da ta funkcija išče po "
"celotnem zapisu vsakega stika; iskanje <quote>and</quote> lahko vrne ne le "
"Andyja Browna in Andrewa Jonesa, temveč tudi Billa Smitha (ki dela za "
"gradbeno podjetje Brown and Root)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Search</quote> function."
"</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona funkcije <quote>Search</quote> v &kaddressbook;."
"</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Search</quote> function.</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona funkcije <quote>Search</quote> v &kaddressbook;.</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1690
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Search</quote> function in action."
msgstr "Funkcija <quote>Išči</quote> &kaddressbook; v akciji."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[ (All)&nbsp;<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>]"
msgstr ""
"[ (Vse)&nbsp;<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tool performs a filtering function, based on categories. The two "
"default categories are <quote>Untagged</quote> and <quote>Groups</quote>. "
"You can create new categories by associating <quote>Tags</quote> of your own "
"devising with particular contact records (see <link linkend=\"edit-basic-info"
"\">Add New Contact</link> in chapter 4, above). Clicking either "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> button "
"will set the selected categories to <quote>None</quote>; the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-refresh."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> button "
"will reset the selection criteria to <quote>All</quote>."
msgstr ""
"To orodje izvaja funkcijo filtriranja na podlagi kategorij. Dve privzeti "
"kategoriji sta <quote>Neoznačeno</quote> in <quote>Skupine</quote>. Nove "
"kategorije lahko ustvarite tako, da določenim zapisom stikov pripišete "
"<quote>Oznake</quote>, ki si jih sami izmislite (glejte <link linkend=\"edit-"
"basic-info\">Dodaj nov stik</link> v poglavju 4 zgoraj). S klikom na gumb "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> bodo "
"izbrane kategorije nastavljene na <quote>Nič</quote>; gumb "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-refresh."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> bo "
"merila izbire ponovno nastavil na <quote>Vse</quote>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Filter</quote> function."
"</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona funkcije <quote>Filter</quote> funkcije "
"&kaddressbook;.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Filter</quote> function.</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona funkcije <quote>Filter</quote> funkcije "
"&kaddressbook;.</phrase>"

