msgstr "Funkcija <quote>Filter</quote> &kaddressbook; v akciji."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1733
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Context Menus"
msgstr "Kontekstni meni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1735
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click the &RMB; anywhere inside the main Text Area, a context menu "
"will appear, as illustrated below. The particular menu that appears depends "
"on both the panel within which the right-click occurred and the particular "
"data item that was selected, if any."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete &RMB; kjer koli znotraj glavnega besedilnega območja, se prikaže "
"kontekstni meni, kot je prikazano spodaj. Posebni meni, ki se prikaže, je "
"odvisen od plošče, na kateri je bil klik z desno tipko miške, in od "
"morebitnega izbranega podatkovnega elementa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1740
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Address Book Context Menu"
msgstr "Kontekstni meni imenika"

