"\">chapter 2</link>, above."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost kontekstnega menija zažene pogovorno okno <quote>Dodaj imenik</"
"quote>, ki je dokumentirano v <link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-address-book"
"\">poglavje 2</link>, zgoraj."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:1784
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete Address Book"
msgstr "Izbriši imenik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choosing this context menu option will delete the selected address book. Be "
"careful!"
msgstr ""
"Z izbiro te možnosti kontekstnega menija izbrišete izbrani imenik. Bodite "
"previdni!"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"press\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-"
"refresh.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Update "
"Address Book Folder</guimenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"press\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-"
"refresh.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Posodobi "
"mapo imenika</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This context menu option forces &kaddressbook; to reload the contact data "
"associated with the selected address book."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost kontekstnega menija prisili &kaddressbook;, da ponovno naloži "
"podatke o stikih, povezane z izbranim imenikom."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:1799
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder Properties..."
msgstr "Lastnosti mape..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1800 index.docbook:1807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This context menu option displays summary information about the selected "
"address book."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost kontekstnega menija prikaže povzetek informacij o izbranem "
"imeniku."

#. Tag: guimenu
